          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The decay of the photoproducts was counted",
                "with two NaI(Tl) detectors mounted on either side of",
                "the sample. The detectors were shielded from",
                "synchrotron generated background by a large iron and",
                "concrete wall. Only pairs of pulses from the",
                "detectors which were in coincidence were accepted.",
                "The data acquisition cycle included a bombardment",
                "period of 20 sec and a counting period of 45 sec",
                "duration. During the counting period, electron",
                "injection into the synchrotron was blocked."
              ]
            }
